text: Eglė Raznauskaitė (born 16 September 1997) is a Lithuanian footballer who plays as a midfielder for Jonava. She has been a member of the Lithuania women's national team. ==References== Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:Lithuanian women's footballers Category:Lithuania women's international footballers
